als in the Electric Vehicles sector (Truflation Guest Post)</div><div class="growing-line-wrapper"><div class="growing-line"></div></div></div><div fs-cmsfilter-field="excerpt" class="desktop-body2">This week, we bring on Stefan Rust, CEO of Truflation, as a guest author for our Macro Research Bites series. We dive into industrial metals like lithium, copper, cobalt, nickel and palladium – many of which will soon be tradable as perpetuals on Ostium – and explore their significance to the growing Electric Vehicles sector.</div></div></a><div class="top"><div class="collection-list-wrapper w-dyn-list"><div role="list" class="collection-list w-dyn-items"><div role="listitem" class="collection-item w-dyn-item"><div class="w-embed"><a data-w-id="1ab270ea-040d-6ac3-9daf-d4eb96b37774" href="/blog?tags=Commodities" class="link-block blog-tag-wrap w-inline-block">
